---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Donations - Ramy Ghorayeb"
  description="NGOs I Support Monthly"
>
  <div class="fade-in">
    <!-- Page Title -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16">Donations</h1>

    <!-- Donations Content -->
    <section class="max-w-2xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-secondary">
          We are paid fairly well in tech. I give back a small portion of my income to my favorite NGOs - organizations full of people dedicating their days to charitable work we often overlook. These are the ones I donate monthly to. I hope you can find one in this list that inspires you to start or increase your contribution.
        </p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse text-secondary">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-primary dark:bg-[#1F1F1F]">Type</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-primary dark:bg-[#1F1F1F]">NGO</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-primary dark:bg-[#1F1F1F]">Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.doctorswithoutborders.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Doctors Without Borders</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Doctors can make a lot of money if they want to but these ones decide to save the people in need instead. One of the few organizations that prioritize medical independence over government grants.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.redcross.org.lb/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Lebanese Red Cross</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">The country has been living through a forever-crisis: the 2019 financial crisis, the 2020 port explosion then the Covid crisis, the 2022-2025 war. This is the most reliable and transparent organization in Lebanon to donate to.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.restosducoeur.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Restos du Coeur</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Maybe the most scrutinized NGO in France. Provides a social safety net for those in need in the country.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Environment</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.rainforesttrust.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Rainforest Trust</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">They focus on land acquisition for high efficiency with low overhead.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Corruption</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.anticor.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Anticor</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Some of the most courageous people in France, fighting public corruption despite government pressure. They are responsible for the first-ever conviction of a former French President (Chirac case, 2011) for embezzling public funds.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Tech</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.laquadrature.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Quadrature du Net</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Hardline defenders of privacy in the EU. They led in 2021 the GDPR charge that resulted in a €746 million fine —at the time, the largest in history—for non-consensual advertising targeting.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Tech</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.wikipedia.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Wikipedia</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Free, crowdsourced encyclopedia maintaining the world's knowledge accessible to everyone.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default dark:border-[#2F2F2F]">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Tech</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://archive.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline text-link">Internet Archive</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">A Library of Alexandria that's actually real. They are currently fighting for their legal life.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
